// _dev/answer-keys/<dept>.json by `node _dev/build-answer-keys.js`), inside
// this serverless function whose source is never served to a client.
//
// Security properties:
//  - Department is derived from the request HOST, never the body — one
//    agency's client cannot request another agency's grading data.
//  - The caller's Supabase JWT is verified against that department's own
//    Supabase project before any grading happens (each department has an
